The propagation speed of the electromagnetic wave in the medium, i.e., the phase velocity of the wavefront

\[
\begin{gathered}
\omega t - \beta z = \text{constant} \\
v = \frac{\mathrm{d} z}{\mathrm{~d} t} = \frac{\omega}{\beta}
